#install.packages("gridExtra")
library(gridExtra)
## Warning: package 'gridExtra' was built under R version 3.3.2
p1 = ggplot(aes(x = friend_count), data = pf) +
  geom_histogram() 

p2 = ggplot(aes(x = friend_count), data = pf) +
  scale_x_log10() +
  geom_histogram() 

p3 = ggplot(aes(x = friend_count), data = pf) +
  scale_x_sqrt() +
  geom_histogram()
